            "rating": 5,
            "title": "Great for travel and camping.",
            "content": "<p>I usually use electrolyte drops and monk fruit sweetener at home, but these little packets are great for travel and camping so I don't need to pack the bottles. The powder is VERY sweet... too much for me, but I just use half the packet in my bottle, which is perfect. The flavor is great and the hydration is great.</p>",
