          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Rectangle_49_4.png",
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 5,
            "title": "Works well for my needs",
            "content": "<p>I love this flavor. It ain’t gotta multivitamin undertone/after-taste. Great for hot/humid regions, gyms/sports, and even my plasma donation prep. I do not get the same nauseating feeling I got with others I’ve tried.</p>",
